source.name: Social Security Administration Percentage of Fast-Track Receipts for Fiscal Year 2010 and 2011
source.description: The dataset provides the percentage of fast-track receipts by state during the reporting fiscal year 2010 and 2011. Fast-tracked cases consist of those cases identified as Quick Disability Determination (QDD), Compassionate Allowance (CAL), or both.
